            "codex": "$wiki-topic-verifier Verify docs/wiki/runtime/retry-policy.md and docs/wiki/runtime/index.md against raw/processed/retry-guidance.md, including leaf granularity, source links, leaf-link evidence, lint, and OKF validation."
